{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_23972114.mp3", "duration": 3.36, "text": "Vienas pla\u010diausiai naudot\u0173 naikintuv\u0173."}
