{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_23985025.mp3", "duration": 3.216, "text": "\u0160iaudai naudojami gyvuli\u0173 kraikui."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24008530.mp3", "duration": 2.916, "text": "M\u0117go ra\u0161yti eil\u0117ra\u0161\u010dius."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24302377.mp3", "duration": 3.996, "text": "Raudoname lauke sidabrin\u0117 juosta."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24302395.mp3", "duration": 4.536, "text": "Senov\u0117je \u010dia stov\u0117jo \u0160lienavos dvaras."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24302406.mp3", "duration": 4.428, "text": "Paveikslai daugiausia nutapyti ant metalo."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24330588.mp3", "duration": 4.788, "text": "Rytuose siekia Vilniaus\u2013\u0160iauli\u0173 gele\u017einkel\u012f."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24330595.mp3", "duration": 3.06, "text": "Jie prasid\u0117jo nuo ketvirtfinalio."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24532484.mp3", "duration": 5.976, "text": "Up\u0117 u\u017etvenkta statant Minge\u010devyro hidroelektrin\u0119."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24624566.mp3", "duration": 2.556, "text": "Vaidmuo gali tur\u0117ti vard\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24624592.mp3", "duration": 2.88, "text": "Kaune jidi\u0161 kalba."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_24685546.mp3", "duration": 4.356, "text": "Seniau b\u016bta dvaro."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25073166.mp3", "duration": 3.816, "text": "Trumpai teritorij\u0105 kontroliavo danai."}
