{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25111081.mp3", "duration": 4.86, "text": "Motina kilusi i\u0161 Kli\u0161i\u0173 dvaro."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25111123.mp3", "duration": 3.636, "text": "Pakra\u0161\u010diu prateka Magdalena."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25111134.mp3", "duration": 3.06, "text": "Buvo daug su\u017eeist\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25111152.mp3", "duration": 6.768, "text": "V\u0117liau jis prad\u0117jo supaprastinti savo vaizdavimo formas iki dideli\u0173 vientisos spalvos plot\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25111164.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "Mieste populiariausia sporto \u0161aka beisbolas."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25113484.mp3", "duration": 3.636, "text": "Ta\u010diau \u0161alyje tvarkos nebuvo."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25115028.mp3", "duration": 3.204, "text": "T\u0117vai buvo ateistai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25115627.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "Miestelio pastatai beveik nenukent\u0117jo."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25115741.mp3", "duration": 3.528, "text": "D\u016bminis kvarcas rudos spalvos."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25116022.mp3", "duration": 2.556, "text": "Visi jie \u017euvo."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25116936.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "Dauguma j\u0173 blogai tirpsta vandenyje."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25116972.mp3", "duration": 2.556, "text": "Yra keli uostai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25116993.mp3", "duration": 3.888, "text": "Sub\u016br\u0117 nema\u017e\u0105 b\u016br\u012f kra\u0161totyros darbuotoj\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25117504.mp3", "duration": 3.528, "text": "Jung\u0119 da\u017enai darydavo i\u0161 a\u0161ut\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25117575.mp3", "duration": 2.988, "text": "Jis \u012fsteig\u0117 na\u0161lai\u010di\u0173 prieglaud\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25118467.mp3", "duration": 2.196, "text": "Visiems i\u0161\u0117jo po lygiai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25118532.mp3", "duration": 3.6, "text": "Pastarieji du \u0161achmatininkai \u017eaid\u0117 tarpusavyje."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25119202.mp3", "duration": 4.5, "text": "Jau debiutin\u0117se savo var\u017eybose \u012fmu\u0161\u0117 \u012fvart\u012f."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25119431.mp3", "duration": 3.816, "text": "Anyk\u0161\u010di\u0173 literat\u0173 klubo narys."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25119442.mp3", "duration": 3.672, "text": "Baig\u0117 Nemaj\u016bn\u0173 vidurin\u0119 mokykl\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25119469.mp3", "duration": 3.204, "text": "Buvo nutarta statyti nauj\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25119489.mp3", "duration": 4.14, "text": "\u0160iaurin\u0117je pakrant\u0117je plyti dirbami laukai."}
