{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25125608.mp3", "duration": 3.096, "text": "Tana laivuojama \u017eemupyje."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25125610.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "Ji pakeit\u0117 ankstesn\u0119 \u0160ima\u0161kio dinastij\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25125776.mp3", "duration": 3.708, "text": "Kartais nurodomi kiti tikslai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25125847.mp3", "duration": 3.456, "text": "I\u0161nykimo prie\u017eastys neai\u0161kios."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25140065.mp3", "duration": 2.808, "text": "Tai yra vad."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25174952.mp3", "duration": 3.888, "text": "Dz\u016bkijos Lions klubo narys."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25174953.mp3", "duration": 3.456, "text": "Iki \u0161iol yra \u017einoma \u0161v."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25175105.mp3", "duration": 4.176, "text": "Jie turi dukr\u0105 vardu Anahita."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25175213.mp3", "duration": 2.448, "text": "Snukis tamsiai pilkas."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25175281.mp3", "duration": 2.52, "text": "Taip pat yra \u0161v."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25175718.mp3", "duration": 4.716, "text": "\u010cempionais tapo lietuviai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176124.mp3", "duration": 4.14, "text": "Tada aortos vo\u017etuvai u\u017esidaro."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176216.mp3", "duration": 4.176, "text": "V\u0117liau Dvor\u017eakas gr\u012f\u017eo \u012f Prah\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176474.mp3", "duration": 6.156, "text": "Turi gerai i\u0161sivys\u010diusias gal\u016bnes."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176476.mp3", "duration": 4.536, "text": "Tuo pat metu \u012fk\u016br\u0117 ansambl\u012f \u201eBob\u0173 vasara\u201c."}
