{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176805.mp3", "duration": 4.5, "text": "Jis buvo paveiktas japoni\u0161ko grafikos meno."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176831.mp3", "duration": 3.636, "text": "Vik\u0161rai randami ant sen\u0173 \u0105\u017euol\u0173 \u0161ak\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25176834.mp3", "duration": 3.348, "text": "\u0160iandien tai yra Zambijos Respublika."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25177577.mp3", "duration": 3.42, "text": "Vyrauja \u017ealieji plotai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25178066.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "Film\u0105 platino \u201eDreamworks\u201c."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25178466.mp3", "duration": 3.78, "text": "\u010cempionatas prasid\u0117jo ne\u012fprastai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25181812.mp3", "duration": 3.456, "text": "\u0160e\u0161tojo de\u0161imtme\u010dio Venecija."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25181813.mp3", "duration": 4.788, "text": "Pavaldus valstybinei Vidaus vandens keli\u0173 direkcijai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25183630.mp3", "duration": 4.428, "text": "Nustatyta dvide\u0161imt plutonio izotop\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25189085.mp3", "duration": 3.276, "text": "Jie kasami ruden\u012f arba pavasar\u012f."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25189086.mp3", "duration": 5.508, "text": "Dluskio sukil\u0117li\u0173 b\u016brys vienas pirm\u0173j\u0173 \u012fsitrauk\u0117 \u012f sukilim\u0105 Lietuvoje."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25190027.mp3", "duration": 4.896, "text": "Asmuo turi tur\u0117ti vidurin\u012f i\u0161silavinim\u0105."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25190074.mp3", "duration": 5.616, "text": "Kulkosvaid\u017eiuose nuo seno naudojami \u0161autuv\u0173 \u0161oviniai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25190340.mp3", "duration": 4.14, "text": "Savo teises \u012f kra\u0161t\u0105 parei\u0161k\u0117 ir lenkai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25190367.mp3", "duration": 3.348, "text": "Kai kurie \u0161unys turi odos problem\u0173."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25190980.mp3", "duration": 5.796, "text": "Tai buvo vad."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25191276.mp3", "duration": 5.22, "text": "Jis ceitnote \u017eaid\u0117 puikiai."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25193337.mp3", "duration": 3.348, "text": "Lizd\u0105 suka \u017eemai kr\u016bmuose."}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/jasontitus/finetuneparakeet/data/cv25_lt/cv-corpus-25.0-2026-03-09/lt/clips/common_voice_lt_25195110.mp3", "duration": 3.24, "text": "Taip pat yra du kupolai."}
